reviewText:
If you are a Rock 'n Roll history freak....this is a MUST SEE. Especially enjoyed his interviews with Richard Thompson, otherwise known as "England's Best Kept Secret". I bought the DVD when seeing  Davy Knowles perform
 at the Greeley Blues Music Festival here in Colorado...thinking it looked interesting when I saw Richard Thompson's name. Wasn't sure what exactly to expect...but I was blown away. Very well done...& extremely informative.
